1. VRM

Fixed Effect Models

Investigating categorical Hum_Dist Vs. various regions

  1. VRM ~ year and human disturbance gradient (categorical- 3 levels)

  2. VRM ~ year and island side (leeward/windward)

  3. VRM ~ year and region 3 (3 options)

  4. VRM ~ year and region 4 (4 options)

  5. VRM ~ year and region.full (5 options- Site 32 as Mid-Lagoon only site in that category)

  6. VRM ~ year and region.kb (4 options, my personal choices given my site locations (N.Lagoon, S.Lagoon, Vaskes Bay, BOW))

#Models looking at different regions
m.vrm <- lm(vrm ~ year + hum_dist, data = mpq) #Hum_Dist = Categorical
